WEBVTT

00:00.300 --> 00:01.900
What kind of sports do you like to play?

00:02.500 --> 00:05.350
I play soccer and basketball for fun on the weekends...

00:05.800 --> 00:07.200
...and I play baseball, too.

00:08.050 --> 00:11.200
We have a neighborhood pickup game twice a month. It's really fun!

00:12.300 --> 00:14.700
And I also play tennis with my brother sometimes.

00:15.600 --> 00:17.900
How about you? Do you play any sports?

00:18.500 --> 00:21.800
I like to do archery and karate. I'm working on my green belt now.

00:22.200 --> 00:24.600
I also go golfing with my dad when I get a chance.

00:24.850 --> 00:26.200
You should come with us sometime.

00:26.600 --> 00:28.800
Sure, I'd like to learn how to play golf.

00:29.250 --> 00:30.800
And you should come play tennis with us!

00:31.300 --> 00:32.200
Sounds good!

